continuum-skin-desc:
E lava hau fili fa'ahiga Continuum e lua:
* 11 - Te Continuum fo'ou aki tona sino mo me'a gaue fo'ou.
*  - Te Continuum ne'e fau tonu fakatahi mo te [[mw:gaue fakafo'ou]] ote Kautahi Vikimetia.
prefs-continuum-enable-continuum-1-help: Hoki fetogi te sino o te Continuum i te 'u ta'u ka hoko mai. E lave pe tau faka'aoga te Continuum āfea (o Tesepeli 19). Ki he fakakātoa o te 'u logo, vaka'i te [[mw:Reading/Web/Desktop_Improvements|pāsina gaue]].
continuum-opt-out-tooltip: Fetogi tau fakatu'utu'u ki hau liliu ki re Continuum āfea
continuum.css: /* Ko CSS fuli i heni e faka'asi ānai ke sio ki ai nātou e faka'aoga te Continuum */
continuum.js: /* Ko te 'atu JavaScript i heni e faka'asi ānai kia nātou e faka'aoga'i te Continuum */
continuum-language-button-aria-label: 'Alu ki he fakamatala i he tahi lea. E ma'u i te {{PLURAL:$1|lea e $1|lea e$1}}
continuum-no-language-button-aria-label: E tohi pe te fakamatala i te lea aeni. Fakaliliu ki ni tahi 'u lea.
continuum-search-loader: Kua vave asi mai te fua o te kumi
continuum-anon-user-menu-pages: Pāsina o nātou kua mavae ki tu'a
